Inside, various firmsincluding consulting, cybersecurity, data science, and healthcarecompete for attention with glossy case study booklets and promotional items. Students engage with human resources teams at kiosks to upload resumes while rehearsing their elevator pitches, clutching resumes in branded folders. Workshops on networking etiquette and technical interview strategies are ongoing in an adjoining classroom. A cybersecurity company conducts a laptop-based password cracking challenge, and a robotics startup draws interest by flying a small drone overhead. Alumni volunteers offer motivational talks near a coffee station enriched by the aroma of coffee and catered snacks, while event staff manage registrations, log attendance metrics, and display employer interviews on a whiteboard, with announcement chimes signaling the event's final hour.

Alumni participate in a panel discussing preparation for technical interviews, while volunteers offer motivational talks near a coffee station where catered snacks fill the air. Workshops on networking etiquette take place in an adjoining classroom. Consulting and finance firms enhance the environment with glossy case study booklets displayed on high tables. A data science company presents a live dashboard of fair attendance, and a cybersecurity company hosts an interactive password cracking challenge on a laptop. Some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall, while a robotics startup captivates attendees with a flying drone, inviting students to a lunchtime pitch session. Event staff manage registrations and distribute lanyards, capturing the experience on camera.

Career center staff log attendance metrics, and international students seek guidance on visa sponsorship requirements, as media teams capture interviews throughout the day. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair.

A robotics startup garners attention by flying a small drone above its booth. Alumni volunteers provide motivational talks and participate in panel discussions on technical interview preparation near a coffee station, filled with the aroma of coffee and catered snacks. Workshops on networking etiquette and interview strategies are conducted in an adjoining classroom. Event staff manage registrations, log attendance metrics, and provide assistance to international students seeking advice on visa sponsorship, all while media crews capture interviews throughout the event.
